          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The absolute  differential cross section was obtained",
                " with the aid of such quantities as effective  number",
                " of  C-12  nuclei  per cm**2,  the solid angle of the",
                " neutron detector (14.6 msr),  the number  of  tagged",
                " photons,  the  neutron-detection efficiency for each",
                " neutron energy,  and the neutron-attenuation factor.",
                " In  order to derive the cross sections to ground and",
                " low-lying excited states  of  C-11,  gaussians  were",
                " fitted   to  neutron  spectra.  The  gaussians  were",
                " centered at energies of E-exc = 0, 2.0, 4.6 (average",
                " of 4.3 and 4.8),  6.5, and 8.1 MeV, corresponding to",
                " low-lying states in C-11."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Statistical errors."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Systematic errors were estimated as 7% due to",
                " neutron-detection  efficiency,  6%  due  to  neutron",
                " scattering   correction,   and  3%  due  to  tagging",
                " efficiency"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The corrections were made for scattering of neutrons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A measurements of the differential photoneutron cross",
                " section of C-12 at 65-degrees,  between Eg = 30  and",
                " 100 MeV are reported.  Tagged photons,  monocromatic",
                " to within 2.6 mev,  were  used,  thus  allowing  the",
                " cross sections to a wide range of final states to be",
                " observed."
              ]
            }
          ],
